      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## What's Changed\n\n- Added configurable OpenAI-compatible provider settings, including API base URL, outline model, chapter model, and optional max completion tokens.\n- Added separate course and chapter concurrency settings for rate-limited providers.\n- Added retry handling, truncated-response detection, failed chapter reports, and resume support.\n- Added localized command and ribbon labels for supported output languages.\n- Improved the settings layout and updated the demo screenshot.\n\n## Notes\n\n- Desktop ribbon tooltips update immediately after changing language.\n- Obsidian mobile toolbar and ribbon management labels may require an app restart because those labels are cached by Obsidian internals.\n\n## Release Assets\n\n- main.js\n- manifest.json\n- styles.css\n",
